text: The following lists events that happened during 2003 in the Democratic Republic of São Tomé and Príncipe. ==Incumbents== *President: Fradique de Menezes *Prime Minister: Maria das Neves ==Events== *January 22: President Fradique de Menezes dissolved parliament over disagreements related to issues of presidential power.President Dissolves Parliament, IRIN *July 16-23: An attempted coup d'état took place ==Sports== *Inter Bom Bom won the São Tomé and Príncipe Football Championship ==References== Category:Years of the 21st century in São Tomé and Príncipe Category:2000s in São Tomé and Príncipe São Tomé and Príncipe São Tomé and Príncipe
title: 2003 in São Tomé and Príncipe
